metadata.description: Basis used in the SMEFTsim_general UFO models, version 3.0.0 or later. Implements Warsaw basis with generic flavor indices for all fermions. $q,u,d$ are the left- and right-handed quark fields. $\ell, e$ are left- and right-handed lepton fields. Quark fields are in the up-aligned basis. Notation and conventions can vary compared to the Warsaw basis paper, see arXiv:2012.11343 for all definitions.
